At the top of the forma click on Permissions 

Then click on New Permission on the dialog that opens. 

Give the permission for the form a name – e.g. Create Issue form 

Select the table to be updated 

Select Global Access (others are role dependent) 

For create forms check Create, Append and Append to (the Append options are for associated tables I.e. attachments. 

For Update and Delete forms select Update or Delete as appropriate. 

Click on Add roles and select the appropriate roles (usually Anonymous user and authenticated users. 

Close the permissions dialog.
